\id 2JN  
\h 2 JOHN 
\toc1 Id ash d John Oꞌohana am Haꞌi ha Wui mo e Wehm e Mihshmad 
\toc2 2 JOHN 
\toc3 2Jn 
\mt1 Id ash d John Oꞌohana am Haꞌi ha Wui mo e Wehm e Mihshmad 
\c 1  
\m  
\v 1-2 Ni-tatchui ni-wepnag: 
\p Am ant wo haꞌichu i em-oꞌohani ahni mani d hema ha wanimeddam wehsijj hegam mo ab si ihm g Jesus Christ. Si ani pihk ni-elid em-hekaj nach pi d t-wehm wohochuddam. Wehs g t-wehm wohochuddam o hab waꞌap si pihk e elid em-hekaj. Pi at hekid gam hu hab wo i e juh g wohokam ab t-amjed. 
\p  
\v 3 Ab o wa si s-em-hoꞌigeꞌid g t-ohg Jiosh g e-alidag Jesus Christ wehm ch ab wo wa baꞌich i em-mah g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam. Kumt ab wo uꞌukchid g wohokam ch wo si pihk e elidad wehs ha hekaj. 
\s1 Matt am oidch hab wo t-junihid g Jiosh chehanig 
\p  
\v 4 Si ani s-ap ni-tahtk ch ia haꞌi ha neid g em-wehm kihkam. K idam an uꞌukch g wohokam hab masma mo ab t-chehani g Jiosh.  
\v 5 Kuni ab wehs i em-gewkemhun mamt ab aꞌai e wui wo si pihk e elidad. Pi o d wechij chehanig ihda mani am em-ahgid. Edgid ach ihda ged hu i shohshon k amjed.  
\v 6 Kutt ab aꞌai t-wui wo si pihk t-elidad ch hekaj am wo t-chehgidad mach ab s-wohog elid ihda chehanigaj g Jiosh. 
\p  
\v 7 Muꞌi at an i wuwha mo chum s-ha mashchamamk g hemajkam ch eda d wabsh s-chu iꞌattomkam ch d obgaj g Jiosh alidag no pi pi ha mashcham mat ia mahsi k d oꞌodham hab masma mach ahchim.  
\v 8 Kumt heg hekaj wo s-e nenꞌoidk mamt pi gam hu hab wo i e juh ab amjed g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga k wabshaba wehs wo bei mo haschu ab em-makiog g Jiosh. 
\p  
\v 9 Hegam matp hedai am gawul wo juh g Jiosh alidag mashchama o pi shaꞌi mahch g Jiosh. S-mahch ach g Jiosh ch ep s-mahch g alidaj ahchim mach am oidch hab masma g alidaj mashchama.  
\v 10 Kumt heg hekaj pi ab hu wo ha kaihamad hegai mat hedai wo chum s-em-mashchamam k eda pi wo ahgachugad g Jiosh alidag mashchama. Pi g am hu wo i ha wahpkid e-kihki ed k chum hems pi hab wo chei ab ha wui. “Jiosh at wo wa em-wehmajk,”  
\v 11 mamt pi ab hu wo i ha wehmt hegam mat am wo ahgachugad g pi wohokam. 
\s1 Mash s-ha neidamk g John ch ha wehm s-neokimk 
\p  
\v 12 Muꞌi ani haꞌichu s-em-ahgidamk ch wabshaba pi id hekaj am i em-oꞌohani nani pi am s-himimk mant wo em-neid k wo em-wehm neo. Kutt am t-wehm si s-ap wo t-tahtkk. 
\p  
\v 13 Ia o haꞌi kih g t-wepnag ch ash si pihk e elid em-hekaj.